{
  "text": "Antisense oligonucleotides (ASOs) were obtained from IONIS Pharmaceuticals as ready-to-inject oligomers, and were used precisely as described previously [CITATION_1] . GW9662 was obtained from Cayman Chemicals (Ann Arbor, MI, #70785).",
